snippet.title: Reese's Pieces Pac-Man
snippet.description: I was on my smartphone using the Snapchat app when this came up.  I am a master of Pac-man.  I wonder about the all time high scores and would dare challenge them.  Playing a game like this with no joystick...I mean, controller is quite tricky, yet natural skill does wonders.   I also like Reese's Pieces candy.  Subscribe to this channel for much, much more, like this video if you do, comment if you wish to, rate it if you think it merits it, share if you think this video is worth such.  And please enjoy.  Have a nice day!
